column1: The Ultimate Module Creator for Magento 2 (UMC2) is a Magento extension that lets you create other magento CRUD modules for your own entities. You can create as many entities as you want in one extension, you can establish relations between them, decide to generate only back-end pages or both back-end and frontend pages.
column2: The Ultimate Module Creator for Magento 2 (UMC2) is a Magento extension that lets you create other magento CRUD modules for your own entities. You can create as many entities as you want in one extension, you can establish relations between them, decide to generate only back-end pages or both back-end and frontend pages.

column1:
UMC generates the code in a 'human readable' form. It's easier to figure out what the code is about when the variables and methods have a propper name.
For example it's easier to read foreach ($_posts as $_post){...} or $_post->getTags() than foreach ($_list as $_item){...} or $_entity->getRelated('tags');
The value you fill in here will be used for variable names, file names and table names.
